; Regression test for issue #1634: Metadata/Note contents can't include
; a ledger formatted date (BZ#562)
;
; Querying tags whose values contain slashes (e.g. dates like
; 2011/08/30) failed because the query predicate serializer wrapped mask
; values in /.../ without escaping internal slashes, causing the
; expression parser to misinterpret them as regex delimiters.

2014/05/01 * Business Trip
    ; trip: 2011/08/30 Corona
    Expenses:Travel    $500.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg tag trip="2011/08/30 Corona"
14-May-01 Business Trip         Expenses:Travel             $500.00      $500.00
                                Assets:Cash                $-500.00            0
end test
